ministic constraints, absolute auditable state transitions, and high-throughput execution tracks.\n49 |             </p>\n50 |             <p className=\"text-white/70 leading-[1.7] text-[14.5px] font-light font-sans\">\n51 |               Our engineering philosophy is forged from the discipline of industrial automation—where safety margins are non-negotiable, and sub-millisecond reliability is the baseline expectation. We don't just build agents; we build the pipelines that make them trusted assets.\n52 |             </p>\n53 |           </div>\n54 |         </div>\n55 |       </section>\n56 | \n57 |       {/* Core Values System */}\n58 |       <section className=\"relative w-full px-6 lg:px-16 pb-16 border-t border-white/5 pt-16\">\n59 |         <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto\">\n60 |           <div className=\"text-center max-w-[800px] mx-auto mb-12\">\n61 |             <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.2em] text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">Inviolable Pillars</span>\n62 |             <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[34px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">Our Operating Core</h2>\n63 |           </div>\n64 | \n65 |           <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n66 |             {values.map((val) => (\n67 |               <div key={val.title} className=\"p-6 rounded-[20px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/40 hover:border-[#E4000F]/20 transition-all\">\n68 |                 <div className=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\">{val.icon}</div>\n69 |                 <h3 className=\"text-[17px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight\">{val.title}</h3>\n70 |                 <p className=\"mt-3 text-[13px] leading-[1.6] text-white/60 font-light font-sans\">{val.desc}</p>\n71 |               </div>\n72 |             ))}\n73 |           </div>\n74 |         </div>\n75 |       </section>\n76 | \n77 |       {/* Premium CTA */}\n78 |       <section