e verified that the responsive design is flawless, with mobile views being fully polished. Spacing, typography, and visual hierarchy also meet the criteria.\n\n\n**Verifying Design Integrity**\n\nI've just finished verifying the design's integrity. I've performed checks to ensure all requirements are met. The site remains fully aligned with the requirements, and I've confirmed adherence to the \"do not\" directives, such as avoiding backend elements, fake data, and unauthorized modifications to the landing page. Everything is outstandingly complete and well-designed!\n\n\n"}}
